{"id": "art-138", "label": "Art. 138", "title": "Art. 138: Dispoziţii generale", "slug": "art-138", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 138: Dispozi&#355;ii generale </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1529590263\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2529\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1529590263\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Constituie metode\nspeciale de supraveghere sau cercetare urm&#259;toarele:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_531745470\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2528\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_531745470\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)interceptarea comunica&#355;iilor ori a oric&#259;rui tip\nde comunicare la distan&#355;&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_837612919\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2527\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_837612919\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)accesul la un sistem informatic;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1019768532\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2526\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1019768532\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)supravegherea video, audio sau prin fotografiere;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_438196893\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2525\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_438196893\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)localizarea sau urm&#259;rirea prin mijloace tehnice;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1914753592\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2524\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1914753592\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)ob&#355;inerea datelor privind tranzac&#355;iile\nfinanciare ale unei persoane;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1302000603\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2523\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1302000603\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)re&#355;inerea, predarea sau perchezi&#355;ionarea\ntrimiterilor po&#351;tale;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_968344448\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2522\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_968344448\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)utilizarea investigatorilor sub acoperire &#351;i a\ncolaboratorilor;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1407394550\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2521\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1407394550\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>h)participarea autorizat&#259; la anumite\nactivit&#259;&#355;i;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_22477731\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2520\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_22477731\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>i)livrarea supravegheat&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_620978409\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2519\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_620978409\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>j)ob&#355;inerea datelor de trafic &#351;i de localizare\nprelucrate de c&#259;tre furnizorii de re&#355;ele publice de comunica&#355;ii\nelectronice ori furnizorii de servicii de comunica&#355;ii electronice\ndestinate publicului.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1899232287\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2518\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1899232287\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Prin interceptarea comunica&#355;iilor ori a\noric&#259;rui tip de comunicare se în&#355;elege interceptarea, accesul,\nmonitorizarea, colectarea sau înregistrarea comunic&#259;rilor efectuate prin\ntelefon, sistem informatic ori prin orice alt mijloc de comunicare.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)Prin acces la un sistem\ninformatic se în&#355;elege p&#259;trunderea într-un sistem informatic sau\nmijloc de stocare a datelor informatice fie direct, fie de la\ndistan&#355;&#259;, prin intermediul unor programe specializate ori prin\nintermediul unei re&#355;ele, în scopul de a identifica probe.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(4)Prin sistem informatic se\nîn&#355;elege orice dispozitiv sau ansamblu de dispozitive interconectate ori\naflate în rela&#355;ie func&#355;ional&#259;, dintre care unul sau mai multe\nasigur&#259; prelucrarea automat&#259; a datelor, cu ajutorul unui program\ninformatic.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(5)Prin date informatice se\nîn&#355;elege orice reprezentare de fapte, informa&#355;ii sau concepte sub o\nform&#259; adecvat&#259; prelucr&#259;rii într-un sistem informatic, inclusiv\nun program capabil s&#259; determine executarea unei func&#355;ii de c&#259;tre\nun sistem informatic.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(6)Prin supraveghere video, audio\nsau prin fotografiere se în&#355;elege fotografierea persoanelor, observarea\nsau înregistrarea conversa&#355;iilor, mi&#351;c&#259;rilor ori a altor\nactivit&#259;&#355;i ale acestora.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(7)Prin localizare sau urm&#259;rire\nprin mijloace tehnice se în&#355;elege folosirea unor dispozitive care\ndetermin&#259; locul unde se afl&#259; persoana sau obiectul la care sunt\nata&#351;ate.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(8)Prin perchezi&#355;ionarea\ntrimiterilor po&#351;tale se în&#355;elege verificarea, prin mijloace fizice\nsau tehnice, a scrisorilor, a altor trimiteri po&#351;tale sau a obiectelor\ntransmise prin orice alt mijloc.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1053948101\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2517\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1053948101\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)Prin ob&#355;inerea datelor privind tranzac&#355;iile\nfinanciare ale unei persoane se în&#355;elege opera&#355;iunile prin care se\nasigur&#259; cunoa&#351;terea con&#355;inutului tranzac&#355;iilor financiare\n&#351;i al altor opera&#355;iuni efectuate sau care urmeaz&#259; s&#259; fie\nefectuate prin intermediul unei institu&#355;ii de credit ori al altei\nentit&#259;&#355;i financiare, precum &#351;i ob&#355;inerea de la o\ninstitu&#355;ie de credit sau de la alt&#259; entitate financiar&#259; de înscrisuri\nori informa&#355;ii aflate în posesia acesteia referitoare la tranzac&#355;iile\nsau opera&#355;iunile unei persoane.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1466053833\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2516\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1466053833\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(10)Prin utilizarea investigatorilor sub acoperire &#351;i\na colaboratorilor se în&#355;elege folosirea unei persoane cu o alt&#259;\nidentitate decât cea real&#259; în scopul ob&#355;inerii de date &#351;i\ninforma&#355;ii cu privire la s&#259;vâr&#351;irea unei infrac&#355;iuni.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1964371311\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2515\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1964371311\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(11)Prin <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>participarea\nautorizat&#259; la anumite activit&#259;&#355;i</i> se în&#355;elege comiterea\nunei fapte similare laturii obiective a unei infrac&#355;iuni de corup&#355;ie,\nefectuarea de tranzac&#355;ii, opera&#355;iuni sau orice fel de în&#355;elegeri\nprivind un bun sau privind o persoan&#259; despre care se b&#259;nuie&#351;te\nc&#259; ar fi disp&#259;rut&#259;, c&#259; este victima traficului de persoane\nori a unei r&#259;piri, efectuarea de opera&#355;iuni privind droguri sau\nsubstan&#355;e dopante, precum &#351;i prestarea unui serviciu,\ndesf&#259;&#351;urate cu autorizarea organului judiciar competent, în scopul\nob&#355;inerii de mijloace de prob&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_879194379\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2514\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_879194379\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(12)Prin <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>livrare\nsupravegheat&#259;</i> se în&#355;elege tehnica de supraveghere &#351;i\ncercetare prin care se permit intrarea, circula&#355;ia sau ie&#351;irea de pe\nteritoriul &#355;&#259;rii a unor bunuri în privin&#355;a c&#259;rora\nexist&#259; o suspiciune cu privire la caracterul ilicit al de&#355;inerii sau\nob&#355;inerii acestora, sub supravegherea ori cu autorizarea\nautorit&#259;&#355;ilor competente, în scopul investig&#259;rii unei\ninfrac&#355;iuni sau al identific&#259;rii persoanelor implicate în\ns&#259;vâr&#351;irea acesteia.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1023932964\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2513\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1023932964\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(13)Prin <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>supraveghere\ntehnic&#259;</i> se în&#355;elege utilizarea uneia dintre metodele\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (1) lit. a)-d).</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}